{"tid":2088373,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求撚其其鄧紫旗","createTime":"2020-07-01T06:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T07:02:46.000Z","uid":137789,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"076a71a4ef6a3bed72fa590d7c888a016e2fe4cb","tid":2088373,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T06:05:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RmsufQt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRmsufQt.jpg&h=976f1215&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n輕輕鬆鬆鄧梓峰<br />\n求撚其其鄧紫旗"},{"pid":"be3004fccc63a2a2fad884ecf49e7217f0c59967","tid":2088373,"uid":137789,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T06:16:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EZKHAUX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEZKHAUX.png&h=3ce81f8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n襯晒色"},{"pid":"f7269088a4589cff40738a79599647f159c4aab8","tid":2088373,"uid":137789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T06:18:21.000Z","msg":"【社會課】甚麼是警察國家？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1204609\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1204609</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n／／完成了警察國家後，國家就可以不斷的通過新的法律。一些深刻的，定義含糊的法律。只要他願意解釋，每人都會觸犯的法律。使每人每天都在犯法，舉個例子，喝水是犯法。但是執法的嚴寬，卻由執法機關憑喜好去執行。平時服從的人，會被「法律不外乎人情」地開恩。「隻眼開隻眼閉」，有法不執被視為有人情味的表現。對於「麻煩份子」，則把法律看成最嚴刻。每天都可以因為他&quot;犯法&quot;而持續用行政手段玩弄。(其實依那些法律的標準，沒有人不犯法) 不僅法治完全崩潰，而法律本身的信用也完全崩潰。因為大家都知道，重點並不在於你是否有犯法。而是你跟政府的關係如何，關於好你犯法也會視而不見。關係不好，你生存就是犯法。社會走向完全的人治。／／<br />\n<br />\n2020年7月1日<br />\n香港"},{"pid":"67aeff1791953d76df82c085680c327266adcacf","tid":2088373,"uid":62721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be3004fccc63a2a2fad884ecf49e7217f0c59967","tid":2088373,"uid":137789,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T06:16:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EZKHAUX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEZKHAUX.png&h=3ce81f8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n襯晒色"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T06:22:00.000Z","msg":"條八婆應該入面都襯埋紫色一套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a53bbcf10c4637eb57680ff9164dda37fa95652d","tid":2088373,"uid":66609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T06:23:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0785446c376ac5e6c9a11b12639552ed4bae142d","tid":2088373,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67aeff1791953d76df82c085680c327266adcacf","tid":2088373,"uid":62721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be3004fccc63a2a2fad884ecf49e7217f0c59967","tid":2088373,"uid":137789,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T06:16:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EZKHAUX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEZKHAUX.png&h=3ce81f8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n襯晒色"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T06:22:00.000Z","msg":"條八婆應該入面都襯埋紫色一套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T07:02:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sNSFnQo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsNSFnQo.jpg&h=520f37ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲唔係顏色革命？"}]}